					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Couple'a&nbsp;issues</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">I'm&nbsp;pedantic</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p>It possesses the speech mannerisms and personality of the stereotypical Cold War spy</p> </blockquote> <p>Not only do I think this sentence doesn't really make sense, I'd also say it's spoonfeeding the reader a bit.</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-1126 clears its throat</p> </blockquote> <p>Seems a slightly strange thing to say considering you've not put anything in about whether it has a throat or not</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-1126: (shrugs)</p> </blockquote> <p>Same as above</p> <p>Overall it's good enough for an upvote but those were just a couple of nitpicks I had.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
